 describe and evaluate field experiments, correlational designs, quasi experiments, evaluation studies, and survey designs. Coverage of the ethics of social research including the power a researcher wields and tips on how to use it responsibly. "--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aSocial sciencesxResearch. 0aSocial sciencesxMethodology.1 aBrewer, Marilynn B.,d1942-eauthor.1 aLac, Andrew,eauthor.  aH 62 C692 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035196862  aH 62 C692 2015wLCc1i0162035196862d1/3/2017e9/27/2016lON_SHELFmUAHSSn7p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu12/9/201401ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014024004